query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(b1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 10 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('angularjs-directive',
'arraylist',
'backbone.js',
'cmd',
'dplyr',
'entity-framework-4',
'html-table',
'image',
'oracle',
'phpstorm',
'rxjs',
'sass',
'svg',
'wix')
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%me';
